        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Introducing Seth Ingram.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>My Dear Sir,</p>

<p>This will be handed you by <persName>Mr Seth Ingram</persName>&#8212;A gentleman of
high respectability&#8212;and spoken of as a well qualified <persName>surveyor</persName>&#8212;</p>

<p>He visits your <placeName>grant </placeName>to become a <persName>settler</persName>&#8212;Such men cannot but
be valuable to your establishment, and you will derive pleasure in
promoting his interest as far as you can conveniently do so.</p>

<p><persName>Jos H Hawkins</persName></p>

<p><date when="1822-05-30">May 30,1822</date></p>

<p><persName>Judge S. F. Austin</persName></p>


        </div1>
